      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·013.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">Ho pe nung.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>唐棣：栘也。（《羣經治要》卷三），一名常棣、棠棣、鬱李。今名鬱李。
華：花。
肅，敬也。（《羣經治要》卷三）
雝，和也。（《羣經治要》卷三）
曷，何也。（《羣經治要》卷三）</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How great is that luxuriance,
The flowers like those of the peach-tree or the plum!
[See] the grand-daughter of the tranquillizing king,
And the son of the reverent marquis!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
